parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause spontaneous fires, stalling, and loss of vehicle control, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle bursts into flames
the engine stalls without warning
the vehicle loses power
the horn sensors are difficult to locate in emergency situations
an odor of burned wire is present
smoke comes from the steering column
and the vehicle accelerates suddenly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignition system failures can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls without warning
the engine fails to start
the ignition switch exhibits odd and damaging behavior.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Dashboard electrical component failures can cause display malfunctions, leading to driver distraction and potential accidents.
symptoms: The digital A/C display stops functioning
dash lights go out
indicating gear position (neutral
reverse
drive
etc.).

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The automatic transmission slipping or popping can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while shifting gears, which can lead to accidents, especially when merging or crossing traffic. This issue can also cause premature wear on the transmission, leading to costly repairs.
symptoms: The transmission pops or slips when shifting gears
the vehicle hesitates or jerks when accelerating
the transmission fluid level is low
the transmission warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended movement of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or property damage, especially if the vehicle rolls into traffic or pedestrian areas.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts out of park or neutral without the driver's input
the vehicle rolls or moves on its own
the parking brake fails to hold the vehicle in place.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty airbag system can lead to unexpected airbag deployment or failure to deploy in the event of a crash, which can cause serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the airbag deploys randomly or unexpectedly
the airbag fails to deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden and unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle suddenly accelerates
lurches forward
or decelerates rapidly without driver input
resulting in loss of control or crashes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden deceleration or stalling can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle decelerates rapidly while driving
stalls
or loses power
resulting in loss of control or accidents.
